text: Tan Barkley (born 11 December 1965) is a Canadian rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Edmonton
